a Communautu00e9 WordPress\",\"summary\":\"Informations, actualitu00e9s et interviews sur la communautu00e9 WordPress.\",\"poster\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/podlove/image/68747470733a2f2f7777772e7770706f64636173742e6e65742f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f73697465732f352f323032302f30382f7770706f64636173742d7371756172652e706e67/500/0/0/podcast-wordpress-francais\",\"link\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr\"},\"title\":\"WordPress 6.5 Regina\",\"subtitle\":\"Plus de 700 contributeurs, avec plus de 2 500 changements, ont permis la sortie de la derniu00e8re version : WordPress 6.5, alias Regina.\",\"summary\":\"\",\"publicationDate\":\"2024-04-09T00:00:00+00:00\",\"duration\":\"00:06:38.930\",\"poster\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/podlove/image/68747470733a2f2f7777772e7770706f64636173742e66722f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f73697465732f352f323032312f30372f7770706f6463617374626c75652e706e67/500/0/0/21-wordpress-6-5-regina\",\"link\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/podcast/wordpress-6-5-regina/\",\"chapters\":[],\"audio\":[{\"url\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/podlove/file/251/s/webplayer/c/website/wordpress-podcast-fr-e021.mp3\",\"size\":\"9344016\",\"title\":\"MP3 Audio (mp3)\",\"mimeType\":\"audio/mpeg\"}],\"files\":[{\"url\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/podlove/file/251/s/webplayer/wordpress-podcast-fr-e021.mp3\",\"size\":\"9344016\",\"title\":\"WordPress Podcast\",\"mimeType\":\"audio/mpeg\"}],\"contributors\":[{\"id\":\"6\",\"name\":\"Jenny Dupuy\",\"avatar\":\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\",\"role\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"slug\":\"presentateur\",\"title\":\"Pru00e9sentateur\"},\"group\":null,\"comment\":null}]}}, {\"url\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/wp-json/podlove-web-player/shortcode/config/default/theme/wppodcast-blocks\",\"data\":{\"activeTab\":\"chapters\",\"subscribe-button\":null,\"share\":{\"channels\":[],\"outlet\":null,\"sharePlaytime\":false},\"related-episodes\":{\"source\":\"podcast\",\"value\":null},\"version\":5,\"playlist\":\"https://www.wppodcast.fr/wp-json/po